WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.310 --> 00:00:03.330
- Well, I think the cool thing is

2
00:00:03.330 --> 00:00:05.640
we're all familiar with
apps on our phone, right?

3
00:00:05.640 --> 00:00:08.520
And so what I just tell them is like,

4
00:00:08.520 --> 00:00:11.520
imagine if you can make
an app for yourself

5
00:00:11.520 --> 00:00:13.620
and you didn't have to
write a line of code

6
00:00:13.620 --> 00:00:16.440
or know how things work behind the scenes.

7
00:00:16.440 --> 00:00:18.150
What if you could just describe your idea?

8
00:00:18.150 --> 00:00:19.260
And I think it's really cool.

9
00:00:19.260 --> 00:00:22.950
We're at the stage where that's
exactly what you can do now.

10
00:00:22.950 --> 00:00:24.570
You just tell it what you want

11
00:00:24.570 --> 00:00:27.420
and you have this AI thing just going

12
00:00:27.420 --> 00:00:29.020
and building your ideas for you.